  "title": "Clinic Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Clinic Assistant (Full-Time / Part-Time)</strong><br />📍 <strong>Location:</strong> Costa Grove, Pasir Ris<br />📅 <strong>Start Date:</strong> 25 March 2026</p><p>💰<strong> Salary:</strong><br />• Full-time: <strong>$2,400 – $3,400 / month</strong><br />• Part-time: Salary prorated</p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><p>• Billing, payments, Third party insurance claims and MediSave/CHAS claims<br />• Stock management and inventory for medical supplies and pharmacy items<br />• Maintain clinic cleanliness and prepare treatment rooms<br />• General administrative duties (data entry, filing, document scanning, follow-ups, liaising with labs)<br />• Ad-hoc duties to support smooth clinic operations<br />• Provide friendly and professional customer service</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p>• Minimum <strong>1 year</strong> clinic assistant or healthcare admin experience preferred<br />• Minimum GCE N/O / ITE / Diploma (healthcare background is a plus)<br />• Good communication skills and service-oriented attitude<br />• Team player, organised, and willing to learn<br />• Computer literate (Microsoft Office, experience with <strong>Sgimed clinic management system</strong> is an advantage)<br />• Willing to work <strong>weekends and night shifts</strong>, when required<br />• Candidates with more experience may be considered for a <strong>senior role</strong></p><p><strong></strong></p>",
